casebody.data:
No. 126,

Orig.

Kansas v. Nebraska et al. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 532 U. S. 992.]

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $179,064.66 for the period March 1 through October 31, 2001, to be paid equally by the three States.
